videos.description: Wake Forest's John Collins dunks off the pass from Bryant Crawford, and Collins hangs on the rim after the dunk.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Collins dunks and hangs on the rim

videos.description: Virginia's London Perrantes gets the steal, drives down court and makes the difficult reverse layup.
videos.headline: London Perrantes makes a difficult layup

videos.description: Virginia's Isaiah Wilkins blocks Wake Forest's Mitchell Wilbekin's shot at the last possible moment.
videos.headline: Virginia's Wilkins gets the block at the last possible moment

videos.description: Wake Forest's Brandon Childress makes the layup through heavy contact and draws the foul.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Childress lays it up through contact

videos.description: Virginia's Jack Salt perfectly times his jump and dunks down a missed shot from Darius Thompson while getting fouled.
videos.headline: Jack Salt throws down the putback dunk

videos.description: Virginia's London Perrantes hits his fourth 3 pointer against Wake Forest, helping him reach twenty points in the game.
videos.headline: Perrantes hits a 3 to pad the Virginia lead

videos.description: Wake Forest's Keyshawn Woods hits a 3 pointer from the tip of the sword of the Virginia logo.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Woods hits the 3 from deep

videos.description: Virginia's London Perrantes discusses his expanded role on the Cavaliers basketball team and his increased offensive production.
videos.headline: Virginia's Perrantes talks about his role with the team
